<task><p>Verify that the properties are true for these examples by calculating the logs:</p>
<p>Property (1):</p>
    <p><md><mrow>~~~~\log_2 32 = \log_2 (4 \cdot 8) \amp = \log_2 4 + \log_2 8 ~~~~~~~~~~ \text{because} ~2^5 = 2^2 \cdot 2^3)</mrow>
      <mrow><fillin/> \amp = <fillin/> + <fillin/></mrow></md></p>
<p>Property (2):</p>
    <p><md><mrow>~~~~\log_2 8 = \log_2 \left(\dfrac{16}{2} \right)\amp  = \log_2 16 - \log_2 2 ~~~~~~~~~~ \text{because} ~2^3 = \dfrac{2^4}{2^1}</mrow>
    <mrow><fillin/> \amp = <fillin/> - <fillin/></mrow></md></p>
<p>Property (3):</p>
    <p><md><mrow>~~~~\log_2 64 = \log_2 (4^3) \amp = 3\log_2 4 ~~~~~~~~~~  \text{because} ~(2^2)^3 = 2^6</mrow>
    <mrow><fillin/> \amp = <fillin/> \times <fillin/></mrow></md></p></task>

